snippet.title: Tom the postgirl - Cinematic Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist "Tom the postgirl" now on Steam! https://store.steampowered.com/app/2257440/Tom_the_postgirl/

Take a ride with Tom through her village and discover a great deal—perhaps too much—about the locals. Her approach, although controversial, is highly effective: intense and obsessive stalking.

Game by Oopsie Daisies Studio
https://x.com/oopsiedaisiesCH
https://instagram.com/o.opsiedaisies
https://www.tiktok.com/@oopsie.daisies.studio
https://www.oopsiedaisiesstudio.com/

Trailer Crew:
Animation by Kathleen Bohren and Natascha Dübi
Art and direction by Léa Coquoz
Music and SFX by Floris Demandt
